    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "at": {
        "sec": 0.7,
        "frame": 21
      },
      "text": "THE JUNIOR YEAR INTERNSHIP IS THE NEW ENTRY LEVEL JOB.",
      "durationSec": 2.2,
      "style": {
        "font": "sans-serif",
        "color": "white"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "at": {
        "sec": 3.1,
        "frame": 93
      },
      "text": "GETTING AN INTERNSHIP YOUR JUNIOR YEAR IS NOT JUST ABOUT BUILDING YOUR RESUME OR GETTING EXPERIENCE ANYMORE.",
      "durationSec": 5.5,
      "style": {
        "font": "sans-serif",
        "color": "white"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "at": {
        "sec": 8.7,
        "frame": 262
      },
      "text": "IT IS THE ENTRY LEVEL JOB",
      "durationSec": 1.4,
      "style": {
        "font": "sans-serif",
        "color": "white"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "at": {
        "sec": 10.2,
        "frame": 307
      },
      "text": "BECAUSE IF YOU DO WELL DURING THAT SUMMER INTERNSHIP, YOU'LL GET A RETURN OFFER TO COME BACK AFTER GRADUATION.",
      "durationSec": 5,
      "style": {
        "font": "sans-serif",
        "color": "white"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "at": {
        "sec": 15.3,
        "frame": 461
      },
      "text": "IF YOU CAN SECURE THAT THEN YOUR JOB HUNT IS OVER BEFORE YOU EVEN GRADUATE.",
      "durationSec": 3.6,
      "style": {
        "font": "sans-serif",
        "color": "white"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "at": {
        "sec": 19,
        "frame": 572
      },
      "text": "BUT IF YOU MISS THE WINDOW FOR THAT JUNIOR YEAR INTERNSHIP, THEN YOU MIGHT GRADUATE WITH NOTHING LINED UP AND NOW YOU'RE JUST IN THE REGULAR LABOUR POOL.",
      "durationSec": 7.1,
      "style": {
        "font": "sans-serif",
        "color": "white"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "at": {
        "sec": 26.2,
        "frame": 789
      },
      "text": "SO THAT'S WHY IF YOU'RE A FRESHMAN OR A SOPHOMORE, YOU REALLY HAVE TO FOCUS ON SETTING YOURSELF UP FOR SUCCESS TO GET A GOOD INTERNSHIP YOUR JUNIOR YEAR",
      "durationSec": 7,
      "style": {
        "font": "sans-serif",
        "color": "white"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "at": {
        "sec": 33.3,
        "frame": 1003
      },
      "text": "BECAUSE MISSING THAT WINDOW DOESN'T JUST MEAN THAT YOU MISSED OUT ON SOME EXPERIENCE, IT MIGHT MEAN THAT YOU COMPLETELY MISSED OUT ON THE ENTRY LEVEL HIRING BATCH",
      "durationSec": 8.3,
      "style": {
        "font": "sans-serif",
        "color": "white"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "at": {
        "sec": 41.8,
        "frame": 1259
      },
      "text": "AND ARE NOW IN A MUCH POORER POSITION TO TRY AND GET A JOB AFTER YOU GRADUATE.",
      "durationSec": 4.7,
      "style": {
        "font": "sans-serif",
        "color": "white"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "at": {
        "sec": 46.6,
        "frame": 1404
      },
      "text": "SO IF YOU WANNA WORK AT A BIG COMPANY, THE INTERNSHIP PIPELINE MIGHT BE THE ONLY WAY IN.",
      "durationSec": 4.6,
      "style": {
        "font": "sans-serif",
        "color": "white"
      }
